---
// FDIC Official Digital Sign
// Per 12 CFR § 328.5 — as updated by the 2026 Final Rule
// Compliance date: April 1, 2027
// Must be displayed clearly, continuously, and conspicuously
// on the homepage, login page, and deposit account opening page.
// Placed near the top of the page, adjacent to the IDI's name.
---

<dfn class="fdic-digital-sign" aria-label="FDIC-Insured - Backed by the full faith and credit of the U.S. Government">
  <img
    src="/fdic-digital-sign.png"
    alt="FDIC-Insured - Backed by the full faith and credit of the U.S. Government"
    width="550"
    height="44"
    class="fdic-sign-img"
    loading="eager"
  />
  <details class="fdic-details">
    <summary class="fdic-summary" aria-label="Learn more about FDIC insurance">
      <span class="fdic-chevron"></span>
    </summary>
    <div class="fdic-info">
      <p><strong>What is FDIC insurance?</strong></p>
      <p>FDIC insurance protects depositors against the loss of their insured deposits if an FDIC-insured bank or savings association fails. FDIC insurance is backed by the full faith and credit of the United States government.</p>
      <p><strong>Standard insurance amount:</strong> $250,000 per depositor, per insured bank, for each account ownership category.</p>
      <p>
        <a href="https://edie.fdic.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Calculate Your Insurance Coverage &rarr;
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </details>
</dfn>

<style>
  .fdic-digital-sign {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    font-family: "Inter", "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0;
    line-height: 0;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .fdic-sign-img {
    display: block;
    height: 24px;
    width: auto;
    max-width: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .fdic-details {
    display: inline-block;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    white-space: normal;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .fdic-summary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    transition: background 0.15s ease;
  }

  .fdic-summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .fdic-summary:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .fdic-chevron {
    display: block;
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    border-left: 4px solid transparent;
    border-right: 4px solid transparent;
    border-top: 5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .fdic-details[open] .fdic-chevron {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .fdic-info {
    position: absolute;
    top: 100%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    margin-top: 8px;
    min-width: 280px;
    max-width: 360px;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    z-index: 100;
    color: #1a1a2e;
    white-space: normal;
  }

  .fdic-info p {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #374151;
  }

  .fdic-info p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .fdic-info a {
    color: #1a3668;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .fdic-info a:hover {
    color: #c9952a;
  }

  /* Dark variant — when the header has a dark background */
  :global(.fdic-dark) .fdic-digital-sign .fdic-info {
    border-color: #334155;
  }

  /* Mobile: wrapped/stacked layout */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .fdic-digital-sign {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 2px;
    }

    .fdic-sign-img {
      height: 20px;
    }

    .fdic-info {
      left: 0;
      transform: none;
      min-width: 240px;
      max-width: 300px;
    }
  }
</style>
